725232f-b.title: Queens: 34th Avenue - Collins Place
725232f-b.text:
34tk Avedue,north side, east of Collins Place (vantace point).
The view is north along the Whitestone branch of the Long
Islanc Railroad from the awove vantage point toward the
freight station and ice plant at 32nc Avenue.
View 2 shows a closeup of the are near the ice plant and the
gas tank of the Tewtown and rlushing bas Company.
P. B. Sperr  Sarch 3, 1932
